content.rendered:
Directed by K. Raghavendra Rao.

Written by J.K. Bharavi.

Cast Nagarjuna Akkineni(Hathiram Baba). Saurabh Raj Jain(Lord Venkateswara). Anushka Shetty(Krishnamma).Jagapathi Babu.Pragya Jaiswal.Vimala Raman.Rao Ramesh.Brahmanandam.Raghu Babu.Vennela Kishore .Ajay.Tanikella Bharani. Karuna Bhushan(Goddess Anjana Devi).Sai Kumar.Prudhviraj.Sampath Raj.Bharath Reddy.Sana.Sudha.Gundu Sudharshan

Languages Telugu.

Producer A. Mahesh Reddy.

Production Sai Krupa Entertainmen.
